creator: Common Ground Works Sdn Bhd
descriptionHtml:
This app is Common Ground’s coworking community, digitized. Stay connected at all times with the latest benefits, events, business opportunities, and other businesses and members across all of Common Ground’s coworking venues.

With this app, you can:

- Explore and connect with other users through the Newsfeed, Business Opportunities Forum, and Interest Groups

- Browse and attend daily events across social and business spheres

- Browse and redeem partnership benefits across lifestyle and professional sectors

- Book meeting rooms at any venue ahead of time

- Book the best rates for flights, hotels, airport transfer and tours

- Sign up for professional business services customised for your company

Note: You will need to have an account with Common Ground in order to use certain elements of this software.
descriptionShort: Stay connected with benefits, events, business opportunities, and other members.

descriptionHtml:
This app is Common Ground’s coworking community, digitized. Stay connected at all times with the latest benefits, events, business opportunities, and other businesses and members across all of Common Ground’s coworking venues.

With this app, you can:

- Explore and connect with other users through the Newsfeed, Business Opportunities Forum, and Interest Groups

- Browse and attend daily events across social and business spheres

- Browse and redeem partnership benefits across lifestyle and professional sectors

- Book meeting rooms at any venue ahead of time

- Book the best rates for flights, hotels, airport transfer and tours

- Sign up for professional business services customised for your company

Note: You will need to have an account with Common Ground in order to use certain elements of this software.
